/addignore <n>  Add player to ignore list
/unignore <n>   Remove from ignore list
```

### `docs/manual.md` (lines 114-141)

The interactive commands table needs ignore rows after the friend rows.

### `.claude/skills/tuicraft/SKILL.md` (lines 91-102)

The Friends List section needs a parallel Ignore List section with IPC verbs `IGNORED`, `IGNORED_JSON`, `ADD_IGNORE`, `DEL_IGNORE`, and event types `IGNORE_ADDED`, `IGNORE_REMOVED`, `IGNORE_ERROR`.

### `README.md` (line 22)

The "Friends List" bullet in the Features section could be expanded or a new "Ignore List" bullet added.

