## Architecture Summary: Layer-by-Layer

```
UI Input Layer
  src/ui/commands.ts         parseCommand() → Command union type
  src/daemon/commands.ts     parseIpcCommand() → IpcCommand union type

Dispatch Layer
  src/ui/tui.ts              executeCommand() → calls WorldHandle methods
  src/daemon/commands.ts     dispatchCommand() → calls WorldHandle methods

Protocol/Handle Layer
  src/wow/client.ts          WorldHandle interface + worldSession() implementation
                             WorldConn internal state (ignoreStore field)

Handler Layer
  src/wow/world-handlers.ts  handleContactList() → populates ignoreStore
                             handleFriendStatus() → routes to ignoreStore for ignore ops
                             resolveAndDeliver() → filters messages from ignored senders

Store Layer
  src/wow/friend-store.ts    FriendStore (to be mirrored as IgnoreStore)
  src/wow/ignore-store.ts    IgnoreStore (new file, simpler: no status/level/class)

Protocol Parsing Layer
  src/wow/protocol/social.ts parseContactList() (already handles IGNORED flag)
                             buildAddIgnore(), buildDelIgnore() (new functions)

Formatting Layer
  src/ui/format.ts           formatIgnoreList(), formatIgnoreListJson(),
                             formatIgnoreEvent(), formatIgnoreEventObj()
```

