export function buildDelFriend(guid: bigint): Uint8Array
```
For ignore, we need equivalent `buildAddIgnore(name)` and `buildDelIgnore(guid)` — same binary shape as the friend versions (`CMSG_ADD_IGNORE` takes a name cString, `CMSG_DEL_IGNORE` takes a uint64 GUID).

### `/home/openclaw/code/tuicraft/src/wow/protocol/opcodes.ts` (lines 81-88)

```typescript
